        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Public Housing Emergency Response Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes additional assistance from the Public Housing Capital Fund to public housing agencies based upon capital need as determined by the agencies' most recent Physical Needs Assessment.</p>]]>
        </text>
